comment: Hill (LAL) jumps A to B into Green (MEM) and affects his play to the basket.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the game clock is adjusted from 00:51.2 to 00:51.8.
After communicating with the Replay Center, the call on the floor is overturned and the ball is awarded to LAL.
Johnson (LAL) commits a take foul on Conley (MEM).
Hill (LAL) commits a take foul on Gasol (MEM).
Lin (LAL) does not inbound the ball within the allotted 5-second time limit.
Hill (LAL) commits a take foul on Gasol (MEM).
After communicating with the Replay Center, the play is not ruled a clear path foul.
Clarkson (LAL) grabs Conley's (MEM) jersey after the steal, which causes him to fall to the floor.

Green (MEM) briefly clamps Boozer's (LAL) arm and the contact does not prevent him from retrieving the long rebound.
